866
00:36:24,171 --> 00:36:27,021
♪So quiet and distant♪

867
00:36:27,631 --> 00:36:29,951
♪The breeze blows softly♪

868
00:36:29,951 --> 00:36:34,391
♪Scattering at the end of time♪

869
00:36:35,211 --> 00:36:38,571
♪May every blossom here♪

